ery!\u201d They found\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34238,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/07\/06\/abdullah-except-dishonesty\/","url_meta":{"origin":37645,"position":2},"title":"Abdullah on Faith: Believers have many temperaments, except dishonesty","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman ibn Yazid reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThe believer may have all kinds of natural dispositions flowing throughout himself, except for treachery and dishonesty.\u201d Source: al-\u012ama\u0304n li-Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u064a\u064e\u0632\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":110,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/11\/13\/not-allowed-prank-scare\/","url_meta":{"origin":37645,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Pranks: Not allowed to scare another Muslim on purpose","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 13, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Layla reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIt is not lawful for a Muslim to frighten another Muslim.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304w